data.title: George J. Lewis Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about George J. Lewis on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature George J. Lewis including Shane, Docks of New Orleans, and more.
data.text:
The Older Brothers

The Older Brothers is a gang that used to have a notorious reputation. First they hold up Mr. Edwards but end up losing the money. Then they try to get ransom money for Mr. Edwards, but that doesn't go as planned. When they realize that there is a reward being offered for their capture, they turn themselves in for the money, but they are in for a surprise.

Enter the Lone Ranger

Six Texas Ranger are led into an ambush. All are killed except one, who is nursed back to health by a Native American friend from his youth.

Trail's End for a Cowboy

An immature rancher's son forced to sell a herd at a low price tries to make up the difference in a poker game while drunk and loses. Earp refuses to help since no law was broken so the son takes matters into his own hands.
